#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:51
msgid ""
"Each DMN version uses a distinct namespace URI. The validator recognises: "
"DMN 1.3 (`https://www.omg.org/spec/DMN/20191111/MODEL/`), DMN 1.2 (`http://"
"www.omg.org/spec/DMN/20180521/MODEL/`), DMN 1.1 (`http://www.omg.org/spec/"
"DMN/20151101/dmn.xsd`), and the Camunda legacy namespace (`https://"
"www.camunda.org/schema/1.0/dmn`). An unrecognised namespace causes XPath "
"queries in layers 2–5 to fail silently, producing incomplete validation "
"results and unexpected Operaton behaviour."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:51
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:51"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:51
msgid ""
"Update `xmlns` on `<definitions>` to a recognised namespace. For new files, "
"use the DMN 1.3 namespace."
msgstr ""

