msgid "**Rationale**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:101
msgid ""
"Operaton implements the full DMN 1.3 hit policy set but will reject unknown "
"values at deployment time with a cryptic parse error. Catching this before "
"deployment saves a round-trip to the engine."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:101
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:101"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:101
msgid ""
"Correct the `hitPolicy` value on the `<decisionTable>` element. If no hit "
"policy is specified, `UNIQUE` is the default."
msgstr ""

