#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:145
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:145"
msgid "**Rationale**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:145
msgid ""
"An unrecognised output type cannot be mapped to a FEEL type at runtime and "
"cannot be matched against the input types of downstream decisions in a "
"chain. This typically indicates a typo or a custom type name that should be "
"replaced with a standard FEEL type."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:145
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:145"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:145
msgid ""
"Replace the value with a known FEEL type: `string`, `boolean`, `integer`, "
"`long`, `double`, `number`, or `date`."
msgstr ""

