msgid "**Trigger**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:167
msgid ""
"A `<rule>` has a different number of `<outputEntry>` elements than there are "
"`<o>` columns declared on the parent `<decisionTable>`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:167
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:167"
msgid "**Rationale**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:167
msgid ""
"DMN requires at least one `<outputEntry>` per output column per rule. A "
"mismatch means the table is malformed — Operaton will either throw a parse "
"error or produce null output values for the misaligned columns."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:167
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:167"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:167
msgid ""
"Ensure every `<rule>` contains exactly as many `<outputEntry>` elements as "
"there are `<o>` columns in the table."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:176
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:176"
