#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:360
msgid ""
"An `<informationRequirement>` element has neither a `<requiredInput>` nor a "
"`<requiredDecision>` child"
