msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:393"
msgid "**Severity**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:393
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:393"
msgid "🟡 warning"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:393
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:393"
msgid "**Trigger**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:393
msgid ""
"An `<inputExpression>` references a variable name that has no corresponding "
"top-level `<inputData name=\"...\">` declaration in the `<definitions>` "
"element. Not checked for empty expressions, literal booleans (`true` / "
"`false`), or numeric and quoted-string literals — these are hardcoded "
"values, not variable references."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:393
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:393"
msgid "**Rationale**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:393
msgid ""
"Without a matching `<inputData>` declaration, the CPSV Editor cannot "
"discover the DMN's input contract and generates an empty request body on "
"deploy. Adding `<inputData>` elements with `<variable>` children makes the "
"input contract explicit for both tooling and human readers."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:393
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:393"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:393
msgid ""
"For each flagged variable name, add a top-level `<inputData "
"id=\"InputData_<n>\" name=\"<n>\">` element with a `<variable "
"id=\"Variable_<n>\" name=\"<n>\" typeRef=\"<type>\" />` child, placed "
"between `</decision>` and `<dmndi:DMNDI>`."
msgstr ""

